					Objective
				</div>

				<div id="experiment-article-section-3-content" 
					 class="content">
					<p>
					Objective of this experiment is to understand the steps of a Polygon Clipping Algorithm, i.e., how a polygon is clipped so as to render only the part which a user can view.
					As an example, we have demonstrated the steps of Sutherland Hodgeman Algorithm.
					</p>
				</div>

			</section>


